original_title: El Último Hack[er] 2: A Cyberspace Odyssey
overview: In this follow-up to the 2016 hit, Tony is forced to navigate cyberspace, where he will meet new friends and enemies in his search for a way out the web to save the United States of America. Meanwhile, HACKERGAMER2008 gradually infiltrates the White House on its mission to eliminate Hillary Clinton. But... who will be victorious in this battle of skill and hacking?
tagline: THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA NEED YOU
title: El Último Hack[er] 2: A Cyberspace Odyssey
